name: Mackenzie Conservative Allocation ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks a combination of income and moderate long term capital growth. In order to achieve its investment objective, Mackenzie Conservative Allocation ETF invests in global equity and fixed-income securities. The Portfolio Manager seeks to maintain a long-term strategic asset allocation of approximately 40% equity securities and 60% fixed income securities (under normal market conditions).
fulldescription: The ETF seeks a combination of income and moderate long term capital growth. In order to achieve its investment objective, Mackenzie Conservative Allocation ETF invests in global equity and fixed-income securities. The portfolio asset mix may be reconstituted and rebalanced from time to time at the discretion of the Portfolio Manager
